<html:col style="min-width: 197pt;" />
<html:col style="min-width: 8pt;" />
</html:colgroup>
<html:thead>
<html:tr class="header" style="font-size:2pt;-uslm-lc:h1;">
<html:td />
</html:tr>
</html:thead>
<html:tbody style="line-height:8pt; font-size:7pt;">
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style="min-width: 197.0pt; text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Signature of seaman</html:p></html:td><html:td style="min-width: 8.0pt; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Time of service:</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Birthplace</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Months</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Age</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Days</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Height:</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Hospital money</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Feet</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Whole wages</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Inches</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Wages due</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Description:</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Place and time of entry</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Complexion</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Time at which seaman is to</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">  Hair</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;"> be on board</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Wages each month</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">In what capacity</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Wages each voyage</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Allotment payable to</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Advance wages</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Conduct qualifications</html:p></html:td></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;">Amount of monthly</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:right; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;" /></html:tr>
<html:tr style="-uslm-lc:I11;"><html:td style=" text-align:justify; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><html:p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:1em;"> allotment</html:p></html:td><html:td style=" text-align:right; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;" /></html:tr>
</html:tbody>
</html:table>
</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I55" class="indent0 fontsize6"><inline class="small-caps">Note</inline>.—In the place for signature and descriptions of individuals engaged after the first departure of the vessel, the entries are to be made as above, except that the signature of the consul or vice consul, customs officer, or witness before whom the individual is engaged, is to be entered.</p>
